- `apps/sync/ui/events/resources/calls.resource.js` — фабрики (HTTP + WS ops с `commandType`, `createSlice('sync/call_ui')`).
- `apps/sync/ui/modals/sync-call-overlay-modal.js`, `sync-call-incoming-modal.js`.
- `apps/sync/ui/pages/sync-call-join-page.js` — `/sync/join/:linkToken`.
